= Building an Opportunity Ecosystem

Opportunities rarely exist in isolation. They are connected through people, organizations, funding, and community needs.

#compact-flow("Opportunity Ecosystem", (
  ("Community Problem", "Department Responsible", "Budget Allocation"),
  ("Programs & Projects", "Partner Organizations", "Community Impact"),
  ("New Needs Identified", "Future Opportunities"),
))

This cycle repeats continuously. As one problem is addressed, new opportunities emerge.

