= The Day 1 Framework

Everything learned today can be summarized in one interconnected system.

#compact-flow("Day 1 Framework", (
  ("Community Needs", "Public Discussion", "Government Priorities"),
  ("Budget Allocation", "Departments", "Programs & Projects"),
  ("Organizations & Partners", "Community Impact", "New Challenges & Opportunities"),
  ("Community Needs (Cycle Repeats)",),
