#callout("Key lesson")[
  Opportunities are not random. They leave clues.
]

Those clues can be found in:

- Budgets
- Annual reports
- Strategic plans
- Public meetings
- Community conversations
- Organizational partnerships

The best Opportunity Hunters learn how to connect these clues into a complete picture.

When you understand the system, you can identify opportunities before most people even realize they exist.

